   113→            <DialogContent className="w-[95vw] md:max-w-lg max-h-[90vh] md:max-h-[85vh] p-0 gap-0 rounded-xl md:rounded-lg border-none shadow-2xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
   114→                <DialogHeader className="sticky top-0 z-10 bg-background px-4 pt-4 pb-3 border-b shrink-0 text-left">
